partner_signature_species_monsters.name: POMBOMB_NAME
bestiary_bios_localised: Pombombs are universally considered to be one of the friendliest creatures of New Wirral. If it weren’t for their habits of accidentally setting anything and everything on fire, they would make quite good pets.
Pomeranians are a popular breed of domesticated dog. Identifiable for their small size and fluffy coat, they are named for a historical region of Europe south of the Baltic Sea.

initial_moves_moves.name: MOVE_DOG_YEARS_NAME
initial_moves_moves.description_localised: Extends the duration of the target’s status effects.

initial_moves_moves.name: MOVE_STICKY_TONGUE_NAME
initial_moves_moves.description_localised: Hits one target. Lowers the target’s Evasion.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_INFLAME_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Hits one target.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_ZOOMIES_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Hits one target. Takes priority over other moves.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_HOT_POTATO_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Places a bomb on the target that will explode if not immediately passed on by melee contact.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_BOMB_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: A character with Bomb will blow up at the end of their next turn if it’s not passed on by a melee attack.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_ELEMENTAL_WALL_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Sacrifice 20% of HP to create a wall that will absorb up to 3 hits for up to 3 turns.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_BE_RANDOM_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Uses a random move that you have enough AP for.

partner_signature_species_monsters.name: CLOCKSLEY_NAME
partner_signature_species_monsters.description_localised: a toy creature with a long claw arm
bestiary_bios_localised: The Clocksley’s long claw limb gives them a unique advantage in ranged combat, as they are able to wield handheld weaponry at a safe distance. This makes up for the fact that they’re not very fast.

Whilst clockwork machines have existed since ancient history, wind-up toys in particular rose in popularity in the western world in the 1800s. These toys are often “wound” by a key that slots into a keyhole on the toy’s exterior.

initial_moves_moves.name: MOVE_SPRING_LOAD_NAME
initial_moves_moves.description_localised: Automatically gives the user the Spring-Loaded status if they don’t already have it. This turns the user’s melee attack into ranged attacks.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_SPRING_LOADED_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Spring-Loaded extends the range of a character’s melee attacks, turning them into ranged attacks.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_RAISE_ARMS_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Raises the user’s Ranged Attack.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_NAME_RETURN_FIRE
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Chance to be used automatically when hit with a ranged attack.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_BRICK_BLAST_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Hits each member of a team multiple times.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_AP_STEAL_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Steals 1 AP from the target and gives it to the user.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_AP_DONATE_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Shifts all remaining AP from the user to the target.

partner_signature_species_monsters.name: BRUSHROOM_NAME
partner_signature_species_monsters.description_localised: a mushroom with a paintbrush and bandana
bestiary_bios_localised: Brushrooms are keen artists, and paint using the strange pigments that ooze from their heads. It has been observed that they are able to change the physical properties of an object they paint over depending on the colour they use.

As the history of painting is as old as mankind, so too is the history of the paintbrush. Cave paintings from prehistoric civilisation have been found to have been made using tools made of reeds and hairs.

initial_moves_moves.name: MOVE_COATING_PLASTIC_NAME
initial_moves_moves.description_localised: Changes the type of the user or an ally.

initial_moves_moves.name: MOVE_NAME_PAINT_SWIPE
initial_moves_moves.description_localised: Can only be used if the user has a coating active. Hits one target, and transfers the coating onto the target. Always goes last.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_ELEMENTAL_WALL_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Sacrifice 20% of HP to create a wall that will absorb up to 3 hits for up to 3 turns.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_COATING_WATER_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Changes the type of the user or an ally.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_POISON_POLLEN_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Gives the target Poisoned status for 3 turn(s).

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_POISONED_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Poisoned characters take damage at the end of their turn.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_SNOOZE_SPORE_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Gives the target Sleep status for 3 turn(s).

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_SLEEP_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Sleeping characters can’t use the moves they normally have.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_LEECH_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Gives the target Leeched status for 3 turn(s).

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_LEECHED_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Leeched characters take damage at the end of their turn. Opponents are healed by the amount of health taken off.

partner_signature_species_monsters.name: SIRENADE_NAME
partner_signature_species_monsters.description_localised: a winged beast with a microphone tail
bestiary_bios_localised: Sirenades are particularly loud creatures, and can amplify their own singing voices through their microphone tails and wings. They don’t seem to have much awareness as to whether or not their singing is too loud for those around them.

Sirens are creatures from Greek mythology, most prominently appearing in Homer’s Odyssey. They are described as winged bird-like women, who would lure men to their doom with their beautiful and haunting song.

initial_moves_moves.name: MOVE_CALL_FOR_HELP_NAME
initial_moves_moves.description_localised: Chance to summon a temporary ally.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_SONIC_BOOM_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Hits a whole team.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_PROVOKE_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Prevents opponents from directly targeting the user’s allies for 3 turns.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_INTERCEPTING_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Characters with Intercepting intercept all attacks directed at their allies.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_AIR_WALL_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Sacrifice 20% of HP to create a wall that will absorb up to 3 hits for up to 3 turns.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_TAUNT_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Sends the target berserk, forcing it to use only damaging moves for its next 2 turns.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_BERSERK_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Characters with Berserk can only use damaging moves.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_NEW_LEAF_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Removes status effects from the target.

partner_signature_species_monsters.name: KITTELLY_NAME
partner_signature_species_monsters.description_localised: a cat with a broken television head
bestiary_bios_localised: The Kittelly’s only way to communicate is through the static patterns on its television-like “face”. These messages are difficult to decipher, and this hurdle often prevents the common Kittelly from being able to connect with other creatures.
Often associated with witchcraft and the supernatural, the black cat is seen in many cultures as an omen or symbol of bad luck. This reputation is undeserved.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_ZOOMIES_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Hits one target. Takes priority over other moves.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_DOUBLE_SMACK_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Hits one target multiple times.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_ENERGY_SHOT_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Hits one target.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_COPYCAT_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Copies the last move the target used, if you have the AP.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_BROADCAST_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Gives the user Multitarget status for 3 turn(s).

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_MULTITARGET_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Attacks from characters with Multitarget target the whole team.

partner_signature_species_monsters.name: SPIROUETTE_NAME
partner_signature_species_monsters.description_localised: a dancing sea creature with a shell head
bestiary_bios_localised: Spirouettes are advanced mollusc-like creatures. Their major organs all reside in its shell “head”, with its “body” being an extended set of limbs. Its movements are swift and elegant, and they often cloak themselves with seaweed for protection from the elements.
The form of dance and performance known as ballet has its roots in Italy in the 1400s. The word “ballet” itself comes from the Italian “ballare”, meaning “to dance”.

initial_moves_moves.name: MOVE_ICICLE_DART_NAME
initial_moves_moves.description_localised: Hits one target. Uses the user’s Speed stat instead of Ranged Attack.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_WATER_WALL_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Sacrifice 20% of HP to create a wall that will absorb up to 3 hits for up to 3 turns.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_QUICK_SMACK_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Hits one target. Takes priority over other moves.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_COATING_WATER_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Changes the type of the user or an ally.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_TORRENT_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Hits each member of a team multiple times.

tape_upgrades_moves.name: MOVE_FOG_NAME
tape_upgrades_moves.description_localised: Reduces accuracy of ranged attacks that aren’t Water, Air or Ice-type to 0% for 3 turns.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_FOG_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Fog reduces the accuracy of ranged attacks that aren’t Water, Air, or Ice-type to 0%.
